bsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="overflow: hidden; display: inline-block; margin: 0.00px 0.00px; border: 0.00px solid #000000; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); width: 707.50px; height: 886.00px;"><img alt="" src="images/image51.jpg" style="width: 707.50px; height: 886.00px; margin-left: 0.00px; margin-top: 0.00px; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px);" title=""></span></h1><h1 class="c33 c35" id="h.3v5urm2846oo"><span class="c20"></span></h1><h1 class="c33" id="h.5w42u9p0p3b6"><span class="c20">3.Accounts Receivable</span></h1><h2 class="c27" id="h.yeif0xpgsh9f"><span class="c21 c31">3.1 Customer invoice</span></h2><p class="c23"><span class="c10">A Customer Invoice is a binding settlement of outstanding amounts. An invoice is normally created after confirmation that goods have been shipped, or after a service has been performed. ... It contains information such as invoice amount, customer details, supplier details, and terms of payment.</span></p><p class="c23 c17"><span class="c10"></span></p><p class="c23"><span class="c12">The process diagram below gives a brief idea on creating and approving a customer invoice document-</span></p><p class="c4"><span class="c14 c18"></span></p><p class="c13"><span style="overflow: hidden; display: inline-block; margin: 0.00px 0.00px; border: 0.00px solid #000000; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); width: 618.00px; height: 290.10px;"><img alt="" src="images/image107.png" style="width: 618.00px; height: 290.10px; margin-left: 0.00px; margin-top: 0.00px; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px);" title=""></span></p><p class="c4"><span class="c14 c18"></span></p><p class="c4"><span class="c14 c18"></span></p><p class="c13"><span class="c6">1.Transactions </span></p><p class="c13"><span class="c12 c11">To create a &ldquo;Customer Invoice&rdquo;</span></p><p class="c13"><span class="c10 c11">Navigate to &ldquo;Accounts Receivable&ldquo; menu, select &ldquo; Transactions &ldquo; and click on &ldquo;Customer Invoice&rdquo;</span></p><p class="c13"><span class="c10 c11">Upon clicking, all created documents will be listed</span></p><p class="c13"><span style="overflow: hidden; display: inline-block; margin: 0.00px 0.00px; border: 0.00px solid #000000; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); width: 160.00px; height: 147.00px;"><img alt="" src="images/image118.png" style="width: 160.00px; height: 147.00px; margin-left: 0.00px; margin-top: 0.00px; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px);" title=""></span></p><p class="c4"><span class="c10 c11"></span></p><p class="c8"><span class="c10 c11">Viewing or editing the previously created documents can be done here.</span></p><p class="c8"><span style="overflow: hidden; display: inline-block; margin: 0.00px 0.00px; border: 0.00px solid #000000; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); width: 594.00px; height: 221.33px;"><img alt="" src="images/image130.png" style="width: 594.00px; height: 221.33px; margin-left: 0.00px; margin-top: 0.00px; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px);" title=""></span></p><p class="c24"><span class="c10 c11">The following can be done using &ldquo;Acti