><span class="c6"></span></p><p class="c13"><span class="c6">Customer Invoice</span></p><p class="c13"><span class="c12 c11">To approve a &ldquo;Customer Invoice&rdquo;</span></p><p class="c13"><span class="c10 c11">Navigate to &ldquo;Accounts Receivable&ldquo; menu, select &ldquo; Approvals &ldquo; and click on &ldquo;Customer Invoice&rdquo;</span></p><p class="c13"><span class="c10 c11">Upon clicking, all created documents will be listed</span></p><p class="c13"><span style="overflow: hidden; display: inline-block; margin: 0.00px 0.00px; border: 0.00px solid #000000; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); width: 164.00px; height: 112.00px;"><img alt="" src="images/image144.png" style="width: 164.00px; height: 112.00px; margin-left: 0.00px; margin-top: 0.00px; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px);" title=""></span></p><p class="c4"><span class="c14 c18"></span></p><p class="c1 c17"><span class="c0"></span></p><p class="c1 c17"><span class="c0"></span></p><p class="c1 c17"><span class="c0"></span></p><p class="c23"><span class="c21 c18">After clicking the &ldquo;Customer Invoice&rdquo; menu the following window will be displayed where you can see the &ldquo;Not approved&rdquo; and &ldquo;Approved&rdquo; customer invoices. </span></p><p class="c23"><span class="c21 c18">Given below image shows the list of &nbsp;&ldquo;Not approved&rdquo; customer invoices</span></p><p class="c13"><span style="overflow: hidden; display: inline-block; margin: 0.00px 0.00px; border: 0.00px solid #000000; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); width: 624.00px; height: 125.33px;"><img alt="" src="images/image59.png" style="width: 624.00px; height: 125.33px; margin-left: 0.00px; margin-top: 0.00px; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px);" title=""></span></p><p clas