0; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); width: 23.00px; height: 26.00px;"><img alt="" src="images/image9.png" style="width: 23.00px; height: 26.00px; margin-left: 0.00px; margin-top: 0.00px; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px);" title=""></span></li><li class="c2 li-bullet-0"><span class="c12 c11">Print </span><span style="overflow: hidden; display: inline-block; margin: 0.00px 0.00px; border: 0.00px solid #000000; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); width: 29.00px; height: 22.00px;"><img alt="" src="images/image44.png" style="width: 29.00px; height: 22.00px; margin-left: 0.00px; margin-top: 0.00px; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px);" title=""></span></li></ol><p class="c4"><span class="c21 c18"></span></p><p class="c4"><span class="c21 c18"></span></p><p class="c13"><span class="c21 c18">The below image displays the &ldquo; Approved&rdquo; window where the list of &ldquo;Approved&rdquo; customer invoices will be displayed</span></p><p class="c13"><span style="overflow: hidden; display: inline-block; margin: 0.00px 0.00px; border: 0.00px solid #000000; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); width: 594.00px; height: 169.33px;"><img alt="" src="images/image37.png" style="width: 594.00px; height: 169.33px; margin-left: 0.00px; margin-top: 0.00px; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px);" title=""></span></p><p class="c13"><span class="c21 c18">Using the &ldquo;Actions&rdquo; buttons displayed in the right side of the window we can:</span></p><ol class="c16 lst-kix_gnib7je4hir7-0 start" start="1"><li class="c13 c9 li-bullet-0"><span class="c21 c18">Edit the document</span></li><li class="c13 c9 li-bullet-0"><span class="c21 c18">View any attachments related to the order</span></li><li class="c13 c9 li-bullet-0"><span class="c21 c18">Print a copy of the relevant order</span></li></ol><p class="c4"><span class="c6"></span></p><p class="c13"><span class="c32">After a relevant &ldquo;customer invoice &rdquo; document is approved the document process can be traced. In order to trace a document click the &ldquo;Document tracing&rdquo; icon in the &ldquo;Actions&rdquo; tab </span><span style="overflow: hidden; display: inline-block; margin: 0.00px 0.00px; border: 0.00px solid #000000; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); width: 27.00px; height: 18.00px;"><img alt="" src="images/image7.png" style="width: 27.00px; height: 18.00px; margin-left: 0.00px; margin-top: 0.00px; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px);" title=""></span></p><p class="c13"><span class="c21 c18">Upon clicking, the following window will be opened -</span></p><p class="c13"><span style="overflow: hidden; display: inline-block; margin: 0.00px 0.00px; border: 0.00px solid #000000; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); width: 552.00px; height: 269.00px;"><img alt="" src="images/image85.png" style="width: 552.00px; height: 269.00px; margin-left: 0.00px; margin-top: 0.00px; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px);" title=""></span></p><p class="c13"><span class="c21 c18">The above process shows the steps of processing a customer invoice. From the placement of a quotation to customer invoice.</span></p><p class="c4"><span class="c21 c18"></span></p><p class="c13"><span class="c21 c18">The following options can be done to a fully approved customer invoice document</span></p><p class="c13"><span style="overflow: hidden; display: inline-block; margin: 0.00px 0.00px; border: 0.00px solid #000000; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); width: 607.00px; height: 46.00px;"><img alt="" src="images/image145.png" style="width: 607.00px; height: 46.00px; margin-left: 0.00px; margin-top: 0.00px; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px);" title=""></span></p><p class="c13"><span class="c21 c18">In order to view the audit details of the relevant customer invoice, click the &ldquo;Audit&rdquo; option, upon clicking the following window will be displayed</span></p><p class="c13"><span style="overflow: hidden; display: inline-block; margin: 0.00px 0.00px; border: 0.00px solid #000000; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); width: 624.00px; height: 342.67px;"><img alt="" src="images/image94.png" style="width: 624.00px; height: 342.67px; margin-left: 0.00px; margin-top: 0.00px; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px);" title=""></span></p><p class="c13"><span class="c21 c18">In order to GL (General Ledger) review for the relevant customer invoice click the &ldquo;GL review&rdquo; option, upon clicking the following window will be displayed-</span></p><p class="c13"><span style="overflow: hidden; display: inline-block; margin: 0.00px 0.00px; border: 0.00px solid #000000; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); width: 624.00px; height: 284.00px;"><img alt="" src="images/image68.png" style="width: 624.00px; height: 284.00px; margin-left: 0.00px; margin-top: 0.00px; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px);" title=""></span></p><p class="c13"><span class="c21 c18">The above window shows the general ledger description, gl code, transaction amount and other details related to the customer invoice</span></p><p class="c4"><span class="c21 c18"></span></p><p class="c13"><span style="overflow: hidden; display: inline-block; margin: 0.00px 0.00px; border: 0.00px solid #000000; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); width: 624.00px; height: 154.67px;"><img alt="" src="images/image148.png" style="width: 624.00px; height: 154.67px; margin-left: 0.00px; margin-top: 0.00px; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px);" title=""></span></p><p class="c13"><span class="c21 c18">The above window shows the accounts receivable ledger description, invoice number, transaction amount and other details related to the customer invoice</span></p><p class="c4"><span class="c21 c18"></span></p><p class="c4"><span class="c21 c18"></span></p><p class="c4"><span class="c21 c18"></span></p><p class="c5"><span class="c7 c3"></span></p><h2 class="c27" id="h.geg579zbyyse"><span class="c21 c31">3.1 Credit Note</span></h2><p class="c23"><span class="c12">A credit note is a letter sent by the supplier to the customer notifying the customer that he or she has been credited a certain amount due to an error in the original invoice or other reasons.</span></p><p class="c23 c17"><span class="c10"></span></p><p class="c23"><span class="c12">The process diagram below &nbsp;gives a brief idea on creating and approving a credit note document-</span></p><p class="c4"><span class="c14 c18"></span></p><p class="c4"><span class="c14 c18"></span></p><p class="c4"><span class="c6"></span></p><p class="c4"><span class="c6"></span></p><p class="c4"><span class="c6"></span></p><p class="c4"><span class="c6"></span></p><p class="c4"><span class="c6"></span></p><p class="c4"><span class="c6"></span></p><p class="c4"><span class="c6"></span></p><p class="c4"><span class="c6"></span></p><p class="c4"><span class="c6"></span></p><p class="c13"><span style="overflow: hidden; display: inline-block; margin: 0.00px 0.00px; border: 0.00px solid #000000; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); width: 618.00px; height: 258.92px;"><img alt="" src="images/image113.png" style="width: 618.00px; height: 258.92px; margin-left: 0.00px; margin-top: 0.00px; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px);" title=""></span></p><p class="c4"><span class="c6"></span></p><p class="c4"><span class="c6"></span></p><p class="c4"><span class="c6"></span></p><p class="c4"><span class="c6"></span></p><p class="c4"><span class="c6"></span></p><p class="c4"><span class="c6"></span></p><p class="c23"><span class="c29">1.Transactions</span></p><p class="c23"><span class="c12 c11">To create a &ldquo;Credit Note&rdquo;</span></p><p class="c23"><span class="c10 c11">Navigate to &ldquo;Accounts Receivable&ldquo; menu, select &ldquo; Transactions &ldquo; and click on &ldquo;Credit Note&rdquo;</span></p><p class="c23"><span class="c10 c11">Upon clicking, all created documents will be listed</span></p><p class="c13"><span style="overflow: hidden; display: inline-block; margin: 0.00px 0.00px; border: 0.00px solid #000000; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); width: 164.00px; height: 180.00px;"><img alt="" src="images/image20.png" style="width: 164.00px; height: 180.00px; margin-left: 0.00px; margin-top: 0.00px; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px);" title=""></span></p><p class="c4"><span class="c10 c11"></span></p><p class="c8"><span class="c10 c11">Viewing or editing the previously created documents can be done here.</span></p><p class="c8"><span style="overflow: hidden; display: inline-block; margin: 0.00px 0.00px; border: 0.00px solid #000000; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); width: 594.00px; height: 222.67px;"><img alt="" src="images/image126.png" style="width: 594.00px; height: 222.67px; margin-left: 0.00px; margin-top: 0.00px; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px);" title=""></span></p><p class="c24"><span class="c10 c11">The following can be done using &ldquo;Actions&rdquo; tab-</span></p><ol class="c16 lst-kix_f8ri4alpm1y-0 start" start="1"><li class="c2 li-bullet-0"><span class="c12 c11">Edit the relevant credit note</span><span style="overflow: hidden; display: inline-block; margin: 0.00px 0.00px; border: 0.00px solid #000000; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); width: 31.00px; height: 25.00px;"><img alt="" src="images/image19.png" style="width: 31.00px; height: 25.00px; margin-left: 0.00px; margin-top: 0.00px; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px);" title=""></span></li><li class="c2 li-bullet-0"><span class="c12 c11">Attachment </span><span style="overflow: hidden; display: inline-block; margin: 0.00px 0.00px; border: 0.00px solid #000000; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); width: 32.00px; height: 26.00px;"><img alt="" src="images/image8.png" style="width: 32.00px; height: 26.00px; margin-left: 0.00px; margin-top: 0.00px; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px);" title=""></span></li><li class="c2 li-bullet-0"><span class="c12 c11">Print </span><span style="overflow: hidden; display: inline-block; margin: 0.00px 0.00px; border: 0.00px solid #000000; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); width: 29.00px; height: 22.00px;"><img alt="" src="images/image44.png" style="width: 29.00px; height: 22.00px; margin-left: 0.00px; margin-top: 0.00px; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px);" title=""></span></li><li class="c2 li-bullet-0"><span class="c12 c11">History </span><span style="overflow: hidden; display: inline-block; margin: 0.00px 0.00px; border: 0.00px solid #000000; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); width: 21.00px; height: 24.00px;"><img alt="" src="images/image5.png" style="width: 21.00px; height: 24.00px; margin-left: 0.00px; margin-top: 0.00px; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px);" title=""></span></li><li class="c2 li-bullet-0"><span class="c12 c11">Document tracing </span><span style="overflow: hidden; display: inline-block; margin: 0.00px 0.00px; border: 0.00px solid #000000; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); width: 27.00px; height: 18.00px;"><img alt="" src="images/image7.png" style="width: 27.00px; height: 18.00px; margin-left: 0.00px; margin-top: 0.00px; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px);" title=""></span></li><li class="c2 li-bullet-0"><span class="c12 c11">Filter</span><span style="overflow: hidden; display: inline-block; margin: 0.00px 0.00px; border: 0.00px solid #000000; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); width: 37.00px; height: 38.00px;"><img alt="" src="images/image64.png" style="width: 37.00px; height: 38.00px; margin-left: 0.00px; margin-top: 0.00px; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px);" title=""></span></li></ol><p class="c5"><span class="c10 c11"></span></p><p class="c24"><span class="c10 c11">&nbsp;upon clicking the filter icon, &nbsp;the following options will be displayed</span></p><p class="c8"><span style="overflow: hidden; display: inline-block; margin: 0.00px 0.00px; border: 0.00px solid #000000; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); width: 624.00px; height: 101.33px;"><img alt="" src="images/image66.png" style="width: 624.00px; height: 101.33px; margin-left: 0.00px; margin-top: 0.00px; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px);" title=""></span></p><ol class="c16 lst-kix_cbw5amddln21-0 start" start="1"><li class="c2 li-bullet-0"><span class="c10 c11">Select the customer</span></li><li class="c2 li-bullet-0"><span class="c10 c11">Select the confirmation (yes/no)</span></li><li class="c2 li-bullet-0"><span class="c10 c11">Selectthe approval status (yes/no)</span></li><li class="c2 li-bullet-0"><span class="c10 c11">Select the month</span></li><li class="c2 li-bullet-0"><span class="c10 c11">Select the year</span></li><li class="c2 li-bullet-0"><span class="c10 c11">click the filter button to filter results</span></li></ol><p class="c26"><span class="c10 c11">To create a new document click &ldquo;Add Credit Note&rdquo; from the top left corner.</span></p><p class="c8"><span style="overflow: hidden; display: inline-block; margin: 0.00px 0.00px; border: 0.00px solid #000000; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); width: 124.00px; height: 32.00px;"><img alt="" src="images/image25.png" style="width: 124.00px; height: 32.00px; margin-left: 0.00px; margin-top: 0.00px; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px);" title=""></span></p><p class="c36"><span class="c12 c11">Upon clicking, a new window will open. This is the header section of the credit note. The header details should be completed to proceed to add other details to the credit note. Add required details as shown below</span><span class="c7 c3">.</span></p><p class="c8"><span style="overflow: hidden; display: inline-block; margin: 0.00px 0.00px; border: 0.00px solid #000000; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); width: 594.00px; height: 153.33px;"><img alt="" src="images/image147.png" style="width: 594.00px; height: 153.33px; margin-left: 0.00px; margin-top: 0.00px; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px);" title=""></span></p><ol class="c16 lst-kix_vcrz03phzuht-0 start" start="1"><li class="c8 c9 li-bullet-0"><span class="c3 c11">Select a customer - </span><span class="c3">pulled from &ldquo;customer master&rdquo; under &ldquo;system admin&rdquo; menu</span></li><li class="c8 c9 li-bullet-0"><span class="c7 c3">Select the currency type</span></li><li class="c8 c9 li-bullet-0"><span class="c7 c3">Add a comment if necessary</span></li><li class="c8 c9 li-bullet-0"><span class="c3 c11">Financial year -</span><span class="c3">pulled from &ldquo;chart of account&rdquo; under &ldquo;system admin&rdquo; menu</span></li><li class="c8 c9 li-bullet-0"><span class="c3 c11">Financial period - </span><span class="c3">pulled from &ldquo;chart of account&rdquo; under &ldquo;system admin&rdquo; menu</span></li><li class="c8 c9 li-bullet-0"><span class="c7 c3">Document date</span></li></ol><p class="c8"><span class="c7 c3">After entering the relevant details click the &ldquo;Create Credit Note&rdquo; button </span></p><p class="c8"><span style="overflow: hidden; display: inline-block; margin: 0.00px 0.00px; border: 0.00px solid #000000; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); width: 136.00px; height: 32.00px;"><img alt="" src="images/image79.png" style="width: 136.00px; height: 32.00px; margin-left: 0.00px; margin-top: 0.00px; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px);" title=""></span></p><p class="c5"><span class="c7 c3"></span></p><p class="c13"><span style="overflow: hidden; display: inline-block; margin: 0.00px 0.00px; border: 0.00px solid #000000; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); width: 594.00px; height: 129.33px;"><