: 0.00px; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px);" title=""></span></p><p class="c4"><span class="c21 c18"></span></p><p class="c4"><span class="c21 c18"></span></p><p class="c13"><span class="c21 c18">The following can be done to a confirmed pending approval document</span></p><p class="c13"><span style="overflow: hidden; display: inline-block; margin: 0.00px 0.00px; border: 0.00px solid #000000; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); width: 353.00px; height: 64.00px;"><img alt="" src="images/image150.png" style="width: 353.00px; height: 64.00px; margin-left: 0.00px; margin-top: 0.00px; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px);" title=""></span></p><p class="c8"><span class="c7 c3">To view audit related details of a credit note click the Audit&rdquo; option in the header of the &ldquo;edit credit note&rdquo; window. Upon clicking &ldquo;Audit&rdquo; option, the following window will be displayed-</span></p><p class="c8"><span style="overflow: hidden; display: inline-block; margin: 0.00px 0.00px; border: 0.00px solid #000000; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); width: 624.00px; height: 262.67px;"><img alt="" src="images/image23.png" style="width: 624.00px; height: 262.67px; margin-left: 0.00px; margin-top: 0.00px; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px);" title=""></span></p><p class="c19"><span class="c7 c3">The audit window displays details of the relevant person who created and confirmed the credit note. It also shows the confirmation status and last modified date.</span></p><p class="c19"><span class="c7 c3">In order to reopen a pending approval confirmed document click the &ldquo;reopen&rdquo; option form the header</span></p><p class="c19"><span style="overflow: hidden; display: inline-block; margin: 0.00px 0.00px; border: 0.00px solid #000000; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); width: 75.00px; height: 26.00px;"><img alt="" src="images/image22.png" style="width: 75.00px; height: 26.00px; margin-left: 0.00px; margin-top: 0.00px; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px);" title=""></span></p><p class="c19"><span class="c7 c3">Upon clicking the following window will be displayed</span></p><p class="c15"><span class="c7 c3"></span></p><p class="c19"><span style="overflow: hidden; display: inline-block; margin: 0.00px 0.00px; border: 0.00px solid #000000; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); width: 469.00px; height: 471.00px;"><img alt="" src="images/image16.png" style="width: 469.00px; height: 471.00px; margin-left: 0.00px; margin-top: 0.00px; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px);" title=""></span></p><p class="c19"><span class="c7 c3">Enter the relevant comment and click the &ldquo;Reopen&rdquo; button to reopen the pending approval document.</span></p><p class="c15"><span class="c7 c3"></span></p><p class="c5"><span class="c7 c3"></span></p><p class="c4"><span class="c21 c18"></span></p><p class="c4"><span class="c21 c18"></span></p><p class="c13"><span class="c14 c3">The actions buttons-</span></p><p class="c13"><span style="overflow: hidden; display: inline-block; margin: 0.00px 0.00px; border: 0.00px solid #000000; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); width: 102.00px; height: 72.00px;"><img alt="" src="images/image45.png" style="width: 102.00px; height: 72.00px; margin-left: 0.00px; margin-top: 0.00px; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px);" title=""></span></p><p class="c4"><span class="c18 c21"></span></p><ol class="c16 lst-kix_44w3pv2b12qj-0 start" start="1"><li class="c13 c9 li-bullet-0"><span class="c14 c3">Edit the relevant credit note</span></li><li class="c13 c9 li-bullet-0"><span class="c14 c3">View attachment list</span></li><li class="c13 c9 li-bullet-0"><span class="c14 c3">Print the relevant document</span></li><li class="c13 c9 li-bullet-0"><span class="c14 c3">Document tracing</span></li></ol><p class="c4"><span class="c14 c3"></span></p><p class="c13"><span class="c6">The document status can be viewed under the status column</span><span style="overflow: hidden; display: inline-block; margin: 0.00px 0.00px; border: 0.00px solid #000000; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); width: 85.00px; height: 136.00px;"><img alt="" src="images/image33.png" style="width: 85.00px; height: 136.00px; margin-left: 0.00px; margin-top: 0.00px; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px);" title=""></span></p><p class="c4"><span class="c14 c3"></span></p><p class="c4"><span class="c14 c3"></span></p><p class="c4"><span class="c14 c3"></span></p><p class="c4"><span class="c14 c3"></span></p><p class="c4"><span class="c14 c3"></span></p><p class="c4"><span class="c14 c3"></span></p><p class="c4"><span class="c14 c3"></span></p><p class="c4"><span class="c14 c3"></span></p><p class="c4"><span class="c14 c3"></span></p><p class="c4"><span class="c6"></span></p><p class="c13"><span class="c6">2. Approvals</span></p><p class="c4"><span class="c6"></span></p><p class="c13"><span class="c29">Credit Note</span></p><p class="c1"><span class="c12 c11">To approve a &ldquo;Credit Note&rdquo;</span></p><p class="c1"><span class="c10 c11">Navigate to &ldquo;Accounts Receivable&ldquo; menu, select &ldquo; Approvals &ldquo; and click on &ldquo;Credit Note&rdquo;</span></p><p class="c13"><span class="c10 c11">Upon clicking, all created documents will be listed</span></p><p class