="images/image44.png" style="width: 29.00px; height: 22.00px; margin-left: 0.00px; margin-top: 0.00px; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px);" title=""></span></li></ol><p class="c4"><span class="c21 c18"></span></p><p class="c13"><span class="c21 c18">The below image displays the &ldquo; Approved&rdquo; window where the list of &ldquo;Approved&rdquo; credit notes will be displayed</span></p><p class="c1"><span style="overflow: hidden; display: inline-block; margin: 0.00px 0.00px; border: 0.00px solid #000000; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); width: 594.00px; height: 190.67px;"><img alt="" src="images/image47.png" style="width: 594.00px; height: 190.67px; margin-left: 0.00px; margin-top: 0.00px; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px);" title=""></span></p><p class="c13"><span class="c21 c18">Using the &ldquo;Actions&rdquo; buttons displayed in the right side of the window we can:</span></p><ol class="c16 lst-kix_2gmzh8qcdw09-0 start" start="1"><li class="c13 c9 li-bullet-0"><span class="c21 c18">Edit the document</span></li><li class="c13 c9 li-bullet-0"><span class="c21 c18">View any attachments related to the order</span></li><li class="c13 c9 li-bullet-0"><span class="c21 c18">Print a copy of the relevant order</span></li></ol><p class="c4"><span class="c6"></span></p><p class="c4"><span class="c10"></span></p><p class="c4"><span class="c10"></span></p><p class="c4"><span class="c21 c18"></span></p><p class="c4"><span class="c21 c18"></span></p><p class="c13"><span class="c21 c18">The following options can be done to a fully approved customer invoice document</span></p><p class="c13"><span style="overflow: hidden; display: inline-block; margin: 0.00px 0.00px; border: 0.00px solid #000000; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); width: 376.00px; height: 46.00px;"><img alt="" src="images/image122.png" style="width: 376.00px; height: 46.00px; margin-left: 0.00px; margin-top: 0.00px; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px);" title=""></span></p><p class="c13"><span class="c32">In order to view the audit details of the relevant customer invoice, click the &ldquo;Audit&rdquo; option, upon clicking the following window will be displayed</span><span style="overflow: hidden; display: inline-block; margin: 0.00px 0.00px; border: 0.00px solid #000000; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); width: 624.00px; height: 262.67px;"><img alt="" src="images/image23.png" style="width: 624.00px; height: 262.67px; margin-left: 0.00px; margin-top: 0.00px; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px);" title=""></span></p><p class="c4"><span class="c21 c18"></span></p><p class="c4"><span class="c21 c18"></span></p><p class="c13"><span class="c21 c18">In order to GL (General Ledger) review for the relevant customer invoice click the &ldquo;GL review&rdquo; option, upon clicking the following window will be displayed-</span></p><p class="c13"><span style="overflow: hidden; display: inline-block; margin: 0.00px 0.00px; border: 0.00px solid #000000; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); width: 624.00px; height: 238.67px;"><img alt="" src="images/image123.png" style="width: 624.00px; height: 238.67px; margin-left: 0.00px; margin-top: 0.00px; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px);" title=""></span></p><p class="c13"><span class="c21 c18">The above window shows the general ledger description, gl code, transaction amount and other details related to the customer invoice</span></p><p class="c4"><span class="c21 c18"></span></p><p class="c13"><span style="overflow: hidden; display: inline-block; margin: 0.00px 0.00px; border: 0.00px solid #000000; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); width: 624.00px; height: 154.67px;"><img alt="" src="images/image38.png" style="width: 624.00px; height: 154.67px; margin-left: 0.00px; margin-top: 0.00px; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px);" title=""></span></p><p class="c13"><span class="c21 c18">The above window shows the accounts receivable ledger description, invoice number, transaction amount and other details related to the customer invoice</span></p><p class="c4"><span class="c10"></span></p><p class="c4"><span class="c10"></span></p><p class="c4"><span class="c14 c3"></span></p><p class="c4"><span class="c14 c3"></span></p><h2 class="c27" id="h.o3ib5lvd0n4m"><span class="c21 c31">3.1 Receipt Voucher</span></h2><p class="c23"><span class="c12">A Receipt voucher is a receipt for goods or services sold. Receipt Vouchers are of two types: Cash receipt voucher &ndash; It represents receipt of cash in hand. Bank receipt voucher &ndash; It indicates receipt of a cheque or demand draft i.e., money is not received in the form of cash in hand.</span></p><p class="c4"><span class="c14 c18"></span></p><p class="c13"><span class="c32">The process diagram below &nbsp;gives a brief idea on creating and approving a receipt voucher document-</span></p><p class="c4"><span class="c14 c18"></span></p><p class="c13"><span style="overflow: hidden; display: inline-block; margin: 0.00px 0.00px; border: 0.00px solid #000000; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); width: 618.00px; height: 240.96px;"><img alt="" src="images/image74.png" style="width: 618.00px; height: 240.96px; margin-left: 0.00px; margin-top: 0.00px; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px);" title=""></span></p><p class="c4"><span class="c6"></span></p><p class="c4"><span class="c6"></span></p><p class="c13"><span class="c6">1.Transactions</span></p><p class="c13"><span class="c12 c11">To create a &ldquo;Receipt Voucher&rdquo;</span></p><p class="c13"><span class="c10 c11">Navigate to &ldquo;Accounts Receivable&ldquo; menu, select &ldquo; Transactions &ldquo; and click on &ldquo;Receipt Voucher&rdquo;</span></p><p class="c13"><span class="c10 c11">Upon clicking, all created documents will be listed</span></p><p class="c13"><span style="overflow: hidden; display: inline-block; margin: 0.00px 0.00px; border: 0.00px solid #000000; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); width: 163.00px; height: 214.00px;"><img alt="" src="images/image28.png" style="width: 163.00px; height: 214.00px; margin-left: 0.00px; margin-top: 0.00px; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px);" title=""></span></p><p class="c4"><span class="c10 c11"></span></p><p class="c8"><span class="c7 c3">Viewing or editing the previously created documents can be done here.</span></p><p class="c8"><span style="overflow: hidden; display: inline-block; margin: 0.00px 0.00px; border: 0.00px solid #000000; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); width: 594.00px; height: 186.67px;"><img alt="" src="images/image46.png" style="width: 594.00px; height: 186.67px; margin-left: 0.00px; margin-top: 0.00px; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px);" title=""></span></p><p class="c24"><span class="c10 c11">The following can be done using &ldquo;Actions&rdquo; tab-</span></p><ol class="c16 lst-kix_u9559w2kryd2-0 start" start="1"><li class="c2 li-bullet-0"><span class="c12 c11">Edit the relevant purchase request</span><span style="overflow: hidden; display: inline-block; margin: 0.00px 0.00px; border: 0.00px solid #000000; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); width: 31.00px; height: 25.00px;"><img alt="" src="images/image19.png" style="width: 31.00px; height: 25.00px; margin-left: 0.00px; margin-top: 0.00px; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px);" title=""></span></li><li class="c2 li-bullet-0"><span class="c12 c11">Attachment </span><span style="overflow: hidden; display: inline-block; margin: 0.00px 0.00px; border: 0.00px solid #000000; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); width: 32.00px; height: 26.00px;"><img alt="" src="images/image8.png" style="width: 32.00px; height: 26.00px; margin-left: 0.00px; margin-top: 0.00px; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px);" title=""></span></li><li class="c2 li-bullet-0"><span class="c12 c11">Print </span><span style="overflow: hidden; display: inline-block; margin: 0.00px 0.00px; border: 0.00px solid #000000; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); width: 29.00px; height: 22.00px;"><img alt="" src="images/image44.png" style="width: 29.00px; height: 22.00px; margin-left: 0.00px; margin-top: 0.00px; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px);" title=""></span></li><li class="c2 li-bullet-0"><span class="c12 c11">Document tracing </span><span style="overflow: hidden; display: inline-block; margin: 0.00px 0.00px; border: 0.00px solid #000000; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); width: 27.00px; height: 18.00px;"><img alt="" src="images/image7.png" style="width: 27.00px; height: 18.00px; margin-left: 0.00px; margin-top: 0.00px; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px);" title=""></span></li><li class="c2 li-bullet-0"><span class="c12 c11">Filter</span><span style="overflow: hidden; display: inline-block; margin: 0.00px 0.00px; border: 0.00px solid #000000; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); width: 37.00px; height: 38.00px;"><img alt="" src="images/image64.png" style="width: 37.00px; height: 38.00px; margin-left: 0.00px; margin-top: 0.00px; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px);" title=""></span></li></ol><p class="c24"><span class="c10 c11">&nbsp;upon clicking the filter icon, &nbsp;the following options will be displayed</span></p><p class="c24"><span style="overflow: hidden; display: inline-block; margin: 0.00px 0.00px; border: 0.00px solid #000000; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); width: 624.00px; height: 82.67px;"><img alt="" src="images/image58.png" style="width: 624.00px; height: 82.67px; margin-left: 0.00px; margin-top: 0.00px; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px);" title=""></span></p><ol class="c16 lst-kix_6rwl5ndagzob-0 start" start="1"><li class="c2 li-bullet-0"><span class="c10 c11">Select the invoice type</span></li><li class="c2 li-bullet-0"><span class="c10 c11">Select the treasury cleared status</span></li><li class="c2 li-bullet-0"><span class="c10 c11">Select the confirmation (yes/no)</span></li><li class="c2 li-bullet-0"><span class="c10 c11">Selectthe approval status (yes/no)</span></li><li class="c2 li-bullet-0"><span class="c10 c11">Select the cancel status (yes/no)</span></li><li class="c2 li-bullet-0"><span class="c10 c11">Select the month</span></li><li class="c2 li-bullet-0"><span class="c10 c11">Select the year</span></li><li class="c2 li-bullet-0"><span class="c10 c11">click the filter button to filter results</span></li></ol><p class="c5"><span class="c7 c3"></span></p><p class="c8"><span class="c7 c3">To create a new document click &ldquo;Add Receipt Voucher&ldquo; button from the top left corner</span></p><p class="c8"><span style="overflow: hidden; display: inline-block; margin: 0.00px 0.00px; border: 0.00px solid #000000; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); width: 148.00px; height: 32.00px;"><img alt="" src="images/image89.png" style="width: 148.00px; height: 32.00px; margin-left: 0.00px; margin-top: 0.00px; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px);" title=""></span></p><p class="c8"><span class="c7 c3">Upon clicking the button a new window will popup. This is the header section of the Receipt Voucher. Header details should be completed in order to proceed &nbsp;to add additional details to the Receipt Voucher. Add necessary details as shown below</span></p><p class="c8"><span style="overflow: hidden; display: inline-block; margin: 0.00px 0.00px; border: 0.00px solid #000000; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); width: 594.00px; height: 126.67px;"><img alt="" src="images/image67.png" style="width: 594.00px; height: 126.67px; margin-left: 0.00px; margin-top: 0.00px; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px);" title=""></span></p><ol class="c16 lst-kix_d9cv797s9ujz-0 start" start="1"><li class="c8 c9 li-bullet-0"><span class="c7 c3">Select a receipt type ( Customer invoice receipt, Direct receipt and Advance receipt)</span></li><li class="c8 c9 li-bullet-0"><span class="c7 c3">Selecta currency</span></li><li class="c8 c9 li-bullet-0"><span class="c3 c7">Add a narration if necessary</span></li><li class="c8 c9 li-bullet-0"><span class="c3 c11">Financial Year - </span><span class="c3">pulled from &ldquo;chart of account&rdquo; under &ldquo;system admin&rdquo; menu</span></li><li class="c8 c9 li-bullet-0"><span class="c3 c11">Finance period -</span><span class="c3">pulled from &ldquo;chart of account&rdquo; under &ldquo;system admin&rdquo; menu</span></li><li class="c8 c9 li-bullet-0"><span class="c7 c3">Document date</span></li></ol><p class="c8"><span class="c3 c11">After entering the relevant details click the &ldquo;Create Receipt Voucher&rdquo; button </span><span style="overflow: hidden; display: inline-block; margin: 0.00px 0.00px; border: 0.00px solid #000000; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); width: 157.00px; height: 42.00px;"><img alt="" src="images/image34.png" style="width: 157.00px; height: 42.00px; margin-left: 0.00px; margin-top: 0.00px; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px);" title=""></span></p><p class="c8"><span class="c7 c3">Upon clicking, a detailed form will be displayed</span></p><p class="c8"><span style="overflow: hidden; display: inline-block; margin: 0.00px 0.00px; border: 0.00px solid #000000; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); width: 594.00px; height: 208.00px;"><img alt="" src="images/image35.png" style="width: 594.00px; height: 208.00px; margin-left: 0.00px; margin-top: 0.00px; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px);" title=""></span></p><ol class="c16 lst-kix_sz9x7hrwr2vy-0 start" start="1"><li class="c8 c9 li-bullet-0"><span class="c3 c11">Select a bank - </span><span class="c3">pulled from &ldquo;bank master&rdquo; under &ldquo;system admin&rdquo; menu</span></li><li class="c8 c9 li-bullet-0"><span class="c7 c3">Select the relevant bank account</span></li><li class="c8 c9 li-bullet-0"><span class="c7 c3">Select the bank currency</span></li><li class="c8 c9 li-bullet-0"><span class="c7 c3">Enter the cheque number</span></li><li class="c8 c9 li-bullet-0"><span class="c7 c3">Select a type</span></li></ol><p class="c8 c22"><span style="overflow: hidden; display: inline-block; margin: 0.00px 0.00px; border: 0.00px solid #000000; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); width: 336.00px; height: 242.00px;"><img alt="" src="images/image149.png" style="width: 336.00px; height: 242.00px; margin-left: 0.00px; margin-top: 0.00px; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px);" title=""></span></p><ol class="c16 lst-kix_sz9x7hrwr2vy-0" start="6"><li class="c8 c9 li-bullet-0"><span class="c7 c3">Check the box to be VAT applicable</span></li></ol><p class="c5"><span class="c7 c3"></span></p><p class="c8"><span class="c7 c3">Afterwards update the following details</span></p><p class="c8"><span style="overflow: hidden; display: inline-block; margin: 0.00px 0.00px; border: 0.00px solid #000000; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); width: 594.00px; height: 116.00px;"><img alt="" src="images/image104.png" style="width: 594.00px; height: 116.00px; margin-left: 0.00px; margin-top: 0.00px; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px);" title=""></span></p><ol class="c16 lst-kix_ye7nldbhaxxq-0 start" start="1"><li class="c8 c9 li-bullet-0"><span class="c3 c11">Select a GL (General Ledger) account- </span><span class="c3">pulled from &ldquo;chart of account&rdquo; under &ldquo;system admin&rdquo; menu</span></li><li class="c8 c9 li-bullet-0"><span class="c7 c3">Select the relevant department</span></li><li class="c8 c9 li-bullet-0"><span class="c7 c3">Select the client contract type</span></li><li class="c8 c9 li-bullet-0"><span class="c7 c3">Add any comments if necessary</span></li><li class="c8 c9 li-bullet-0"><span class="c7 c3">Enter the amount</span></li></ol><p class="c8"><span class="c7 c3">Once completed, click on &ldquo;Save Changes&rdquo; button </span><span style="overflow: hidden; display: inline-block; margin: 0.00px 0.00px; border: 0.00px solid #000000; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); width: 111.00px; height: 32.00px;"><img alt="" src="images/image75.png" style="width: 111.00px; height: 32.00px; margin-left: 0.00px; margin-top: 0.00px; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px);" title=""></span></p><p class="c5"><span class="c7 c3"></span></p><p class="c5"><span class="c7 c3"></span></p><p class="c8"><span class="c7 c3">Afterwards Select &ldquo;Yes&rdquo; to confirm the document.</span></p><p class="c8"><span style="overflow: hidden; display: inline-block; margin: 0.00px 0.00px; border: 0.00px solid #000000; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); width: 427.00px; height: 153.00px;"><img alt="" src="images/image100.png" style="width: 427.00px; height: 153.00px; margin-left: 0.00px; margin-top: 0.00px; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px);" title=""></span></p><p class="c8"><span class="c7 c3">To view audit related details of a purchase request click the Audit&rdquo; option in the header of the &ldquo;edit receipt voucher&rdquo; window</span></p><p class="c8"><span style="overflow: hidden; display: inline-block; margin: 0.00px 0.00px; border: 0.00px solid #000000; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); width: 297.00px; height: 48.00px;"><img alt="" src="images/image41.png" style="width: 297.00px; height: 48.00px; margin-left: 0.00px; margin-top: 0.00px; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px);" title=""></span></p><p class="c5"><span class="c7 c3"></span></p><p class="c8"><span class="c7 c3">Upon clicking &ldquo;Audit&rdquo; option, the following window will be displayed-</span></p><p class="c8"><span style="overflow: hidden; display: inline-block; margin: 0.00px 0.00px; border: 0.00px solid #000000; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); width: 624.00px; height: 236.00px;"><img alt="" src="images/image17.png" style="width: 624.00px; height: 236.00px; margin-left: 0.00px; margin-top: 0.00px; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px);" title=""></span></p><p class="c19"><span class="c7 c3">The audit window displays details of the relevant person who created and confirmed the purchase request. It also shows the confirmation status and last modified date.</span></p><p class="c15"><span class="c7 c3"></span></p><p class="c19"><span class="c7 c3">In order to reopen a pending approval confirmed document click the &ldquo;reopen&rdquo; option form the header</span></p><p class="c19"><span style="overflow: hidden; display: inline-block; margin: 0.00px 0.00px; border: 0.00px solid #000000; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); width: 75.00px; height: 26.00px;"><img alt="" src="images/image22.png" style="width: 75.00px; height: 26.00px; margin-left: 0.00px; margin-top: 0.00px; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px);" title=""></span></p><p class="c19"><span class="c7 c3">Upon clicking the following window will be displayed</span></p><p class="c15"><span class="c7 c3"></span></p><p class="c19"><span style="overflow: hidden; display: inline-block; margin: 0.00px 0.00px; border: 0.00px solid #000000; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); width: 469.00px; height: 471.00px;"><img alt="" src="images/image16.png" style="width: 469.00px; height: 471.00px; margin-left: 0.00px; margin-top: 0.00px; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px);" title=""></span></p><p class="c19"><span class="c7 c3">Enter the relevant comment and click the &ldquo;Reopen&rdquo; button to reopen the pending approval document.</span></p><p class="c15"><span class="c7 c3"></span></p><p class="c5"><span class="c7 c3"></span></p><p class="c5"><span class="c7 c3"></span></p><p class="c13"><span class="c14 c3">The actions buttons-</span></p><p class="c13"><span style="overflow: hidden; display: inline-block; margin: 0.00px 0.00px; border: 0.00px solid #000000; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); width: 102.00px; height: 72.00px;"><img alt="" src="images/image45.png" style="width: 102.00px; height: 72.00px; margin-left: 0.00px; margin-top: 0.00px; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px);" title=""></span></p><p class="c4"><span class="c21 c18"></span></p><ol class="c16 lst-kix_44w3pv2b12qj-0" start="5"><li class="c13 c9 li-bullet-0"><span class="c14 c3">Edit the relevant credit note</span></li><li class="c13 c9 li-bullet-0"><span class="c14 c3">View attachment list</span></li><li class="c13 c9 li-bullet-0"><span class="c14 c3">Print the relevant document</span></li><li class="c13 c9 li-bullet-0"><span class="c14 c3">Document tracing</span></li></ol><p class="c4"><span class="c14 c3"></span></p><p class="c13"><span class="c14 c3">The document status can be viewed under the &ldquo;status&rdquo; column</span></p><p class="c4"><span class="c14 c3"></span></p><p class="c13"><span style="overflow: hidden; display: inline-block; margin: 0.00px 0.00px; border: 0.00px solid #000000; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); width: 85.00px; height: 136.00px;"><img alt="" src="images/image33.png" style="width: 85.00px; height: 136.00px; margin-left: 0.00px; margin-top: 0.00px; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px);" title=""></span></p><p class="c4"><span 